{"tid":953301,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"醒訓 睡眠質素差","createTime":"2018-12-23T23:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T01:38:18.000Z","uid":154457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1ce74d07a899db3c2ec39ac0508a40f59c171cd4","tid":953301,"uid":154457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T23:44:51.000Z","msg":"訓覺前會不停諗野，要15-30分鐘先可以入睡<br />\n訓個時又好易發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到朝早聽到小小聲就會醒，醒咗仲要訓唔返 <br />\n昨晚1點訓，今朝6點幾7點去個廁所就眼光光，個腦好似開左咁，閂唔到，無晒睡意。<br />\n<br />\n只係想問下有冇人同我一樣，會唔會有方法改善下.....<br />\n<br />\n訓咁少，我真係唔想死住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d0f6b0526202df9e784f2e695e398d4363d9b0","tid":953301,"uid":107840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T01:33:44.000Z","msg":"metoo<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced837a210137c4cd0950ac0a5695a2eb9eaa124","tid":953301,"uid":219446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T01:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}